cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with text extraction and recognition from video clips, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of Neuro-Fuzzy system also suggests a machine learning (cs.LG) approach. Additionally, the paper mentions the diversity of fonts and colors, which indicates a natural language processing (cs.CL) aspect. Finally, the paper mentions video referencing, indexing, and retrieval, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
